serialport_linux
================

An implement of Serialport under linux, writing in C language.

build & run
================

$ make
$ ./a.out

current status
================

serial device: "/dev/ttyUSB0", 
port attribute: 9600, 8, 'N', 1

One thread to write, one thread to read, one thread to exit.

Good luck!

